dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until transfer order confirmation (days)",
    "Time until GI posted (days)",
    "Transfer order created late (%)",
    "GI posted late (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Delivery items with transfer order item created and confirmed") 
        	AS "Time until transfer order confirmation (days)",
		AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Delivery items with goods issue posted") 
        	AS "Time until GI posted (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Delivery items with transfer order created after planned picking date") * 100 
        	AS "Transfer order created late (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Delivery items with goods issue posting later than planned") * 100 
        	AS "GI posted late (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
